'From Squeak3.5 of ''11 April 2003'' [latest update: #5180] on 31 July 2003 at 1:07:02 pm'!"Change Set:		WriteStream-space-tab-fix-jfDate:			31 July 2003Author:			Julian FitzellMake #tab: call #tab instead of duplicating code.Add #space: for parallelism."!!WriteStream methodsFor: 'character writing' stamp: 'JF 7/31/2003 13:01'!space: anInteger 	"Append anInteger space characters to the receiver."	anInteger timesRepeat: [self space]! !!WriteStream methodsFor: 'character writing' stamp: 'JF 7/31/2003 13:00'!tab: anInteger 	"Append anInteger tab characters to the receiver."	anInteger timesRepeat: [self tab]! !